body:
I am writing a web application in GWT,
I am trying to interact with a SOAP web service.
I know how to do it in regular java environment using the JAX-WS library, but GAE (Google App Engine) does not support it.

see [http://groups.google.com/group/google-appengine-java/web/will-it-play-in-app-engine](http://groups.google.com/group/google-appengine-java/web/will-it-play-in-app-engine)

is there a way of consuming a wsdl based web service (ebay web service for example) using GWT+GAE?

Thanks!
title: consuming SOAP web serives in google app engine and GWT
